TestName: [sig-olmv1][OCPFeatureGate:NewOLM][Skipped:Disconnected] OLMv1 operator installation should fail to install a non-existing cluster extension [Suite:openshift/conformance/parallel]
ReasonToAllowInsteadOfFix: The OLMv1 subsystem is new to OCP 4.18. Operator-controller is encountering flakiness when connecting to catalogd securely. The catalogd TLS service certificate is unable to be verified by the service-ca. Manifest changes in certificate loading and extra logs were added to determine the cause of the errors.
